<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4">About Pico Posts</h1>

    <p>Welcome to Pico Posts, where brevity meets expression! Pico Posts is a microblogging platform designed to capture the essence of your thoughts, ideas, and moments in 280 characters or less. Our mission is to provide a space for users to share impactful, concise content and foster meaningful connections within a vibrant community.</p>

    <h2>Our Vision</h2>

    <p>At Pico Posts, we believe that great ideas can be expressed in a few words. In a world filled with information overload, we value the power of simplicity and the impact of concise communication. Our vision is to empower individuals to share their stories, insights, and experiences in a way that resonates with a global audience.</p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Microblogging Excellence:</strong> Craft your messages with precision and creativity in our 280-character limit format.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> Connect with like-minded individuals, discover new perspectives, and engage in conversations that matter.</li>
        <li><strong>Hashtags for Discovery:</strong> Explore trending topics and discover diverse content by following your favorite hashtags.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>

    <p>Pico Posts is committed to maintaining a positive and inclusive environment. We encourage users to express themselves freely while respecting the diversity of our community. Our content policy is designed to ensure that Pico Posts remains a space for constructive communication, creativity, and connection.</p>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>

    <p>Join us in the journey of concise expression! Sign up for a Pico Posts account, customize your profile, and start sharing your thoughts with the world. Whether you're a seasoned microblogger or new to the concept, Pico Posts welcomes you to a platform where every word counts.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>

    <p>Have questions, feedback, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to our support team or connect with us on social media. Thank you for being a part of the Pico Posts community!</p>

    <p class="mb-0">Happy microblogging!</p>
